---
title: Red Pepper Jam Bavette Steak with Garlic Lime Broccoli & Scallion Rice
description: “This meal is my JAM!” That’s what you’ll be saying after just one bite of this savory-sweet pork chop. Red pepper jam blends with chili powder and lime juice to form a tangy pan sauce, in perfect harmony with spiced scallion rice and garlicky roasted broccoli on the side. Flavorful, unique, majorly memorable—yep, this meal’s about to get totally stuck in your head.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/64074e0dfe59f690160f36d7-963b43ac.jpg
